软件包 minijava.intermediate

类摘要
ApplyResource Primary Registers Allocation
Code Intermediate Code Structure
CodeBlock Basic code block in a method, which means there are no jumping instructions within the block except for the last instruction.
CodeStructure Code Structure for Intermediate Code Visitor Return Type
FlowGraph Contains static methods that analyze the intermediate code based on the flow graph of the code structure.
GraphColoringMethod Implements the graph coloring method to optimize register allocation.
InterferenceGraph Graph structure set up for GraphColoringMethod.
IntermediateCode Generate Intermediate Code
IntermediateCodeVisitor Generate Intermediate Code by Visitor
Loop Group of CodeBlock where a path exists between any two of them in the flow graph.
RegCheck Check if register number is invalid
RegLabelLock Register and Goto's Label Lock/Unlock
TargetCode TargetCode contains all Code for current method
